descriptionHtml:
The best free App Lock with Fingerprint support



App lock - The fingerprint lock app helps you lock all your apps. You need to keep your personal information secure, you don't want strangers to access applications on your personal phone, immediately download Lock app, completely free, professional and convenient.

With the App lock fingerprint you can lock your app with your pin, pattern and even your fingerprint. You can also change the method to lock the app whenever you want. Now you no longer have to worry about your personal information being viewed by others by downloading the Applock - App locker application.

Applock - App lock fingerprint can lock all apps in your device:



✔️ Block all social apps, no one will be able to snoop on your private conversations anymore
✔️ Lock application system. System applications such as contacts, messages, collections, etc. can all be easily locked with one click.
✔️ All payment apps will have an extra layer of protection when you use Applock
✔️ Your images and videos will also be viewable only when you set password for app to lock them

✔️ Screen Lock: The screen will never turn off or adjust screen brightness when the app is running
✔️ Uninstallation Prevention: Activate the feature so that others cannot uninstall the App Lock application, the locked applications will be absolutely confidential
✔️Intruder Selfie - Who try to break in my phone?: A photo will be taken and saved here when someone snoops on your apps

Questions & answers:



🤔 Q: How do I use a fingerprint lock?
Answer: App lock fingerprint will work on Android devices running OS 6.0 [Marshmallow] and above and your device supports Fingerprint Recognition.
Go to settings and enable fingerprint lock. After activation, you can use this feature immediately. Be sure to add your fingerprint information to the device beforehand to use this fingerprint lock feature.

🤔 Q: Why should use the "Access to use" permission?
Answer: App Lock uses this permission to detect if an app is locked to launch.

🤔 Q: Does the application consume memory of your device and is it easy to set up and use?
Answer: Applock has a simple interface you can perform any task easily and smoothly.

descriptionHtml:
100% Security with Applock - App lock fingerprint.


Protect your personal data and lock all apps quickly with just one click.


Main features of App lock:


🔐 Lock app:


App lock fingerprint will secure all your information by locking your apps:


    🔒 Applock app can quickly lock social apps like WhatsApp, Instagram, Snapchat, Telegram, TikTok... ensuring absolute data security and privacy.

    🔒 All payment apps like PayPal, Google Wallet... will have an additional security layer when locked with App lock. Minimize risks during payment.

    🔒 You can lock system apps: Contacts, Messages, Gallery,... or any apps on your phone if you have the need for security.

🎑 Hide photos and videos:


The Vault feature will help App lock password hide private photos and videos.


    💎 Hidden photos/videos will not be displayed in the device's gallery, only in the Applock app. That means only you can view them by entering the correct password or fingerprint. From now on, your secret photos/videos will be completely safe.

    Note: To use the Vault feature, Applock needs access to all files (MANAGE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE), and this is the only way to use this feature.

    💎 App lock can also take or record new videos right in the app. Photos/videos after taking will be saved in the hidden photo album of the Applock application. You can experience this useful Hidden Camera feature.

📷 Intruder selfie:


    Capture photos of those who enter wrong password. When enabling this feature, App lock will activate the device's camera and automatically take a photo if someone enters the wrong password. You can review these intrusion photos within this feature. Turn on this feature to enhance phone security.

🎨 Change lock screen themes:


    Diverse theme store, suitable for all interests and personalization needs. You can also easily and quickly customize your lock screen according to your preferences.

🎉 Provide an excellent experience:


    💡 Lock all apps on Android phones with fingerprint, PIN, and pattern. Especially, with fingerprint security feature, unlocking will be extremely convenient and quick.
    (However, Applock only supports fingerprints on Android versions 6.0 and above. Additionally, to use fingerprints, your Android device needs to have hardware for fingerprint sensors, and make sure this sensor is still functional. App lock password will not unlock with fingerprint if your device is running on Android version below 6.0 or does not have a fingerprint sensor or the device's fingerprint sensor is damaged.).

    💡 The app's security system will operate or pause when you click the lock icon on the home screen. In other words, with one click, you will add an additional security layer to the app.

    💡 Easily find apps that need a lock.

    💡 Track locked apps statistics.

    💡 Easily and securely change passwords.

    💡 Don't worry if you forget your password, you can recover it by answering the security question in the Vault feature.

    💡 The app's interface is intuitively designed and easy to use.

Download Applock - App lock fingerprint now to have a fantastic app locking experience.


Applock fingerprint app is currently under development and improvement, so we greatly appreciate your feedback and suggestions via email: applock@app.ecomobile.vn. Your feedback is extremely valuable to help us improve the product.


Sincerely thank you!
